In [[card game]]s, an '''upcard''' is one of two things:

*In [[stud poker|Stud Poker]], an upcard is a card dealt face up to a player and left on the table for others to see. Similarly, in [[casino]] [[blackjack]] the dealer gives himself one card face up for the players to see.
*In the [[Rummy|Rummy family]], an upcard is the top card of the discard pile.

